Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有滑過冰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.60,0:00:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰上流暢的滑冰真是酷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.30,0:00:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次可是有生以來第一次滑冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 超級困難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.40,0:00:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為自己擅長直線滑冰一定沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不時的摔倒、撞到 啊 好痛好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學不會滑冰就會輸給梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.50,0:00:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能就這麼認輸了！了！了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要登上頂峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都會嚮往成為真正的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還從來沒有人能登上那個高峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說只要看了他的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.10,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人的心都會融合到一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.70,0:02:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是什麼樣的人我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 超越我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為真正的明星 真正的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時卡萊多劇團一定會再次振翅高飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於將卡萊多劇團託付給我的蕾拉小姐的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.70,0:03:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非但沒能有回應 還因為我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.20,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉•哈姆雷特也只不過是一個懶散的表演者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓蕾拉小姐這麼被人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.90,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我只有努力讓萊恩承認我作為他的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天一定要他收回對蕾拉小姐說的那些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我對你長久以來一直的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就這麼{\fscx30\fscy110\b1}口{\b0\fscx75\fscy100}羅{\fscx30\fscy110\b1}口{\b0\fscx75\fscy100}羅{\fscx100}嗦嗦說這些\N或許可能會讓你很厭煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那……我剛才說的話你聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要是沒聽到的話……沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也意味著或許你有搞笑的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到梅了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.10,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在將出演《街上的女孩》的會議室裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然太快了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是破例讓她上臺表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為她會認真的幹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅可能不是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是有神秘老師給她特訓去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為失敗所以逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這種人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是新人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒叫就自己進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《街上的女孩》的扮演者都應該在會議室等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有什麼事要發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.50,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩 立刻跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看我真正的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又想搞什麼花樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要讓人看看她真正的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是梅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅很擅長滑冰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那何止是擅長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之精靈王梅又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米娜瑪麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.90,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅表演的是《德古拉》中的米娜瑪麗那個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是米娜瑪麗的角色是使用螺旋回轉的空中飛人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是擅長滑冰也沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的確是在放射著光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.40,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是真正的梅的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修改劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 想怎麼改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《德古拉》改在冰上表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.60,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說選擇我做搭檔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為剛才的表演就能讓我滿意了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的表演很完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你是滿意了 可我覺得很無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒什麼感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看中了滑冰這個點子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.60,0:08:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果米娜瑪麗被刪了 舞臺卻變成了滑冰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我預想的越來越遠了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑冰……啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.80,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也要挑戰滑冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要演米娜瑪麗就得精通滑冰是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說胡話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.50,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你可以在滑冰上贏了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.80,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不試試也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑的不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺擅長直線滑冰的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉不了彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許真的很難 很難 很難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習難度降的太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不象你的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是首先要習慣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背伸直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.90,0:09:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳往旁邊移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再展開點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要倒了~要倒了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就這麼伸展著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和直線滑冰不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將鞋子傾斜了才不容易滑倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就保持這個姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 滑起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的資質很好 很快就能掌握了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅莉羅 在這裏工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡萊多劇團的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我叫苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和梅競爭角色麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識梅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很就沒看到她滑冰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手一點都沒有遲鈍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子如果不在世界的舞臺上大放異彩的話太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界的舞臺上大放異彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅最初來這個滑冰場滑冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在她3、4歲左右的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一眼看到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.70,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得她有走向世界的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠好好練習的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想獲得金牌也不是個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.40,0:10:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子有了另一個夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個遠大的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.20,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我也要和蕾拉小姐一起站在那個舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種想法非常的強烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我怎麼勸她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果她還是沒有聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅那麼崇拜蕾拉小姐……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩看不上我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅很清楚的對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她很喜歡滑冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更喜歡卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.20,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象蕾拉小姐那樣的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起 梅莉羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我穿不了這雙鞋子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年後我畢業了就去參加試演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會和蕾拉小姐一同站在舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你要來看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬著有蕾拉小姐在的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是蕾拉小姐卻引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.60,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會討厭和蕾拉小姐一起表演夢幻超絕技的我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想和她搞好關係的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗澡……啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很煩的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能不要開這種玩笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要這樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的想和空和梅一起……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓梅失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得努力贏她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說要建滑冰場需要3天時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時萊恩會根據滑冰場的情況最終修改劇本劇情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說3天後是測試的最後一次機會了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3天就要學會太亂來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3天之內我一定要學會滑冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要贏梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是認真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.20,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是要求助於梅莉羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅莉羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這不是梅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利羅在滑冰場那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣 再用點力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅莉羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要教空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜託她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想擁有和你對等的競爭能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你不能太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被空超過的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.90,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說空會超過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空很有資質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還在你之上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我會教她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑冰我怎麼可能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且絕對不能輸給空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一定要超過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了梅 也為了蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 你還有弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你自己都沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越熟練了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這就是轉折的關鍵哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體狀況怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在的狀態最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空有弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2天的時間來不及克服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是不說比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天終於要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.20,0:16:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保佑米娜瑪麗的演出者一定是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才練了3天就……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要想合格只靠技術是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的演技還不能說是完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說空會合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:17:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不允許……決不允許發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輸給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒看到那麼努力的梅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯嘛 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只3天時間你想有什麼樣的改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.80,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候表現出來的從容已經完全消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的確是個有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為我的搭檔的話就到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能跳到那種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神技嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空她不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就完成度來說梅更勝一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的這種臨陣磨槍根本談不上完成度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個傢伙身上有些什麼雖然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個時候的確感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.60,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞臺的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對……不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有得到萊恩的承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說梅是萊恩的搭檔了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來演米娜瑪麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是心又不甘也沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.20,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我該做的事就是把《德古拉》演的最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Niagara Diving
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我們的喝彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找了個好的對手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋回轉•跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有著不可思議的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.80,0:22:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人在不知不覺中被你所影響開始放射出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要放射出自己的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.70,0:22:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須克服自己的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的戰鬥才剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底你們誰能成為真正的明星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告\N卡萊多之星新生之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你嚴厲點 空老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.50,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特居然對卡洛斯宣佈說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.20,0:23:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3天之內不學會空中飛人 就要退出卡萊多劇團
